data.description: Attention all buyers! Upgrade your living with this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2300 sq ft home. Completely remodeled in 2021 with new furnace, AC, hot water heater, roof, windows, and siding. Featuring split floor living, open floor plan, large master bedroom with on suite and walk in closet, a 24x36 pole barn with a 12x24 bonus room and 12x24 storage loft. Plus enjoy your 30ft above ground pool installed in 2022, and a large fenced-in backyard. Don't wait, make this dream home yours today! Completely remodeled home in 2021-22, large open concept floor plan with Luxury vinyl flooring, large kitchen island, updated bathrooms, large master bedroom with walk in closet, 24x36 outbuilding with concrete floor & electric, above ground pool, attached garage
